data.description: Welcome home! This spacious 4-bedroom is nestled on a corner lot within a cul-de-sac. The expansive interior boasts a huge family and dining room combo, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. The heart of the home is the kitchen with a dining area and a convenient breakfast bar, making it a culinary enthusiast's delight. Cozy up by the fireplace in the inviting living room, ideal for those chilly evenings. Need a home office or study space? The main level den provides the ideal solution. Upstairs, you'll find a large loft area - perhaps a home gym, playroom, or additional lounge space. With a 3-car garage, there's plenty of space for your vehicles and additional storage. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity.
